{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 180°C. Grease a pie tray with removable bottom (Ø 24 cm approx.) with butter. Line with 4 overlapping sheets of filo pastry or one sheet of puff pastry.","Place milk, egg yolks, sugar and cornflour in mixing bowl and cook <b>8 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>. Transfer to a bowl, let cool and pour over pastry. Sprinkle with cinnamon and set aside.","Place apples, lemon zest and lemon juice in mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>. Remove, pour over cream and bake at 180°C for about 25 minutes or until golden. Serve warm sprinkled with icing sugar."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["butter, unsalted, for greasing","4 sheets filo pastry","400 g milk","3 egg yolks","80 g sugar","30 g cornflour (starch)","1 tsp ground cinnamon","400 g apples (e.g. Reinette), peeled, cored and cut into quarters","1 lemon, grated zest and juice","icing sugar to taste, for sprinkling"]}],"id":"r129352","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-uBwi6fT5P3Q\/XZWfakpBwwI\/AAAAAAAAfEM\/CPE2e42YFUwfk7hES6SdrNIxUP2V8xv1wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ukF6oAQtBc5Jm0bj.png","title":"Easy apple pie","publishedAt":"2017-08-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5 g","fat":"33 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"5 g","calories":"828 kJ \/ 198 kcal"},"usefulItems":"springform tin (Ø 24-26 cm), bowl, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Serve apple pie accompanied with a scoop of ice cream of your choice."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","45m","6 portions"]}